  <answer><![CDATA[<p>Snow sports are great fun but do come with their own risks. Make sure that when you purchase your insurance you consider what activities you will be taking part in. Make sure to think about elements such as;</p>
<p>Off Piste – with or without a guide</p>
<p>Mountain Rescue – Inc. helicopter</p>
<p>Personal Liability – Injuring others</p>
<p>24-hour Emergency Assistance</p>
<p>Other Activities – Tobogganing, local ski racing, snow parks, climbing etc.</p>]]></answer>
